snippet.title: Amber Heard Johnny Depp trial CANCELLED if this happens!?
snippet.description:
#justiceforjohnnydepp
After talking to Lost Beyond Pluto I was able to gain some insight into how Amber Heard could potentially serve jail-time in Australia. This is not guaranteed, but it is possible. It also is possible that Heard may not be extradited(sent back) to the United States to stand trial in Virginia, against Johnny Depp. This raises concern for many. 

Lost Beyond Pluto: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto/videos
My Twitter: iAmDrSoup
